    "Create alert rules for imported assets. When the current price reaches your target, Spectra sends a local notification. Alerts depend on price refreshes from your selected pricing source and fall back to built-in prices when live data is unavailable. Spectra refreshes prices when the app becomes active and on a repeating in-app watch cycle while it stays open." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Create alert rules for imported assets. When the current price reaches your target, Spectra sends a local notification. Alerts depend on price refreshes from your selected pricing source and fall back to built-in prices when live data is unavailable. Spectra refreshes prices when the app becomes active and on a repeating in-app watch cycle while it stays open."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "为已导入资产创建价格提醒规则。当当前价格达到目标值时，Spectra 会发送本地通知。提醒依赖你所选价格源的刷新，并会在实时数据不可用时回退到内置价格。应用激活时以及保持打开期间的循环监视过程中，Spectra 会刷新价格。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "為已導入資產創建價格提醒規則。當當前價格達到目標值時，Spectra 會發送本地通知。提醒依賴你所選價格源的刷新，並會在實時數據不可用時回退到內置價格。應用激活時以及保持打開期間的循環監視過程中，Spectra 會刷新價格。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Create New Wallet" : {
      "localizations" : {
