    "For Bitcoin Cash sends, advanced mode records RBF intent and applies the max-input cap for coin selection." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "For Bitcoin Cash sends, advanced mode records RBF intent and applies the max-input cap for coin selection."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "对于 Bitcoin Cash 发送，高级模式会记录 RBF 意图，并在选币时应用最大输入数量限制。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "對於 Bitcoin Cash 發送，高級模式會記錄 RBF 意圖，並在選幣時應用最大輸入數量限制。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "For Bitcoin sends, advanced mode records RBF/CPFP intent and applies the max-input cap for coin selection." : {
