      }
    },
    "For LTC sends, max input cap is applied for coin selection, RBF policy is encoded in input sequence numbers, and change strategy controls whether change uses a derived change path or your source address." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "For LTC sends, max input cap is applied for coin selection, RBF policy is encoded in input sequence numbers, and change strategy controls whether change uses a derived change path or your source address."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "对于 LTC 发送，选币时会应用最大输入数量限制，RBF 策略会编码到输入序列号中，找零策略决定找零是使用派生找零路径还是原始地址。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "對於 LTC 發送，選幣時會應用最大輸入數量限制，RBF 策略會編碼到輸入序列號中，找零策略決定找零是使用派生找零路徑還是原始地址。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
